    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName ref="#people/51" key="#Popes">Innocentius II</persName>
                        <persName key="#Abbots">Oddoni</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/53"><rs
                                key="#Monasteries">Sancti Sixti</rs></orgName>. Ad exemplar
                            <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/52"> Paschalis II</persName> et
                            <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/54">Calixti II</persName> confirmat
                        provisionem ab eis factam de monasterio Sancti Sixtii et scriptum illud,
                        quod a Calixto II, dum in <rs key="#Geographic_regions">Galliarum
                            partibus</rs> esset, ab illius loci <rs key="#Nuns/sanctimoniales">
                            monialibus</rs> subreptum est, in irritum devocat; censet locum et omnia
                        ad eum pertinentia sub apostolice sedis tutela et protectione servanda a
                        quorumlibet infestantium molestiis libera; confirmat <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">universa praedia</rs> quae <persName
                            key="#Parchment_documents #Queen" ref="#people/55"
                        >Angelberga</persName>, eiusdem monasterii fundatrix, illuc contulit et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">possessionibus</rs> propriis nominibus
                        adnotatas, concedit ius abbatem eligendi a Romano benedicendum <rs
                            key="#Popes">pontifice</rs>, quod si non fuerit in monasterio Sancti
                        Sixti persona idonea de <placeName ref="#places/57" key="#Monasteries"
                                ><orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/67">Casae
                                Dei</orgName></placeName>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">coenobio</rs> eligatur; confirmat quicquid libertatis
                        seu dignitatis praedecessores sui per <rs key="#Papal_concession">authentica
                            privilegiorum scripta</rs> concesserunt; statuit ut <rs key="#Chaplain"
                            >cappellani ecclesiae</rs> Sancti Sixti abbati nihilominus sint subiecti
                        (Ad hoc universalis). Ego Innocentius ecc. Datum <placeName ref="#places/58"
                            >Cremonae</placeName> p. m. <persName key="#Chancellor #Deacons"><name
                                ref="Aimerigus">Aimerici</name></persName>. S. R. E. <rs
                            key="#Chancellor #Deacons">diac. card. et canc.</rs>, II Idus Iulii,
                        indictione X, inc. dom. an. MCXXXIII, pont. Innocentii pp. II an. III. </ab>
                </div>
